{"tid":1505943,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"應承我 將香港語言 文化 精神 同歷史承傳下去","createTime":"2019-08-25T16:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:29:01.000Z","uid":46879,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afdbcb511024d107ea0f190b1ba09123ccba0633","tid":1505943,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日唔講 我怕以後冇機會再講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年 我唔知呢埸仗會唔會贏<br />\n理性去睇 7,000,000同 1,400,000,000比實在係差太遠<br />\n如果輸左 可能面對新疆式嘅再教育同高壓統治<br />\n長遠黎講 中國已經決定唔再俾自由香港 以深圳同上海代替香港 佢哋可能今天仲未做到 但唔難保不久嘅將來做到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我請求大家 要將香港一切語言文化精神歷史傳承下去 </span><br />\n請你務必<span style=\"color: red;\">生出你嘅下一代</span> 人愈多愈好 將香港發生過嘅所有事 香港係一個點嘅地方 香港人引以為傲嘅一切 傳俾下一代<br />\n我地呢代未必完成到嘅大業 唔代表我地下一代 再下一代 再下下一代做唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或許明日香港不復存在 但願香港人永存</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcf8e9c588b9edd94892b79ed123cee28ae96c74","tid":1505943,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"eb9adba429339181c09af7ac992dc71773037c4b","tid":1505943,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"我身雖死 精神猶存"},{"pid":"667893adaccd08460e6bbd0b5b1a7f2f8bf9d06c","tid":1505943,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"鬼國之地 遍草不生"},{"pid":"c3a2b9f2f9a8196063d55b94fd368965b29b018b","tid":1505943,"uid":127379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吊你個街呀!香港人必勝!</span></span>"},{"pid":"df4b5bcdd91f8e7ddbae7f157b3613f30c835956","tid":1505943,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣 公義在人心"},{"pid":"5a7807146950903907838b70ae2b22bc4daf951b","tid":1505943,"uid":36915,